    "description": "Are you a skilled Digital Marketing Manager looking for your next big career move? Tata CLiQ Capital India in Surat offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Tata CLiQ Capital India:\nTata CLiQ Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Tata CLiQ Capital India!",
